    <item>
      <title>Miscellaneous</title>
      <link>https://rxdoi.github.io/miscellaneous/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://rxdoi.github.io/miscellaneous/</guid>
      <description>&lt;ul style=&#34;list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;li style=&#34;margin-bottom: 12px;&#34;&gt;
    I used to participate in algorithm competitions during high school and college.  
    I won a &lt;a href=&#34;https://stats.ioinformatics.org/people/6478&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;gold medal at IOI 2018&lt;/a&gt;.
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li style=&#34;margin-bottom: 12px;&#34;&gt;
    I play a bit of many sports, though I&#39;m not particularly good at any of them — basketball, tennis, badminton, and table tennis, to name a few.
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li style=&#34;margin-bottom: 12px;&#34;&gt;
    I&#39;m deeply passionate about music. I played piano for over a decade during my childhood, and my favorite composers are Beethoven and Chopin.  
    I also enjoy listening to Chinese pop and rock music — see &lt;a href=&#34;https://rxdoi.github.io/mandarin_songs&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; for details.
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li style=&#34;margin-bottom: 12px;&#34;&gt;
    I&#39;m also into some hardcore games, especially roguelike and action titles.  
    My favorite games include &lt;i&gt;DOTA 2&lt;/i&gt;, &lt;i&gt;Slay the Spire&lt;/i&gt;, &lt;i&gt;The Binding of Isaac&lt;/i&gt;, and &lt;i&gt;Elden Ring&lt;/i&gt;.  
    I enjoy playing Japanese Mahjong — I reached the &lt;b&gt;雀圣 (Master)&lt;/b&gt; rank on the platform &lt;i&gt;Mahjong Soul&lt;/i&gt;.  
    Feel free to check out &lt;a href=&#34;https://space.bilibili.com/30626517&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;my Bilibili account&lt;/a&gt; for some of my game clips.
  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
